data.description: Beautiful Home in the Highland Ranch Subdivision.  Recently renovated with updated floorplan!!  New kitchen includes new cabinets, countertops, flooring and appliances.  New flooring and paint in dining room and living room.  All new landscaping with grass, retaining wall, garden area, patio and parking area for RV's and toys!!  New A/C last year and all, but two windows have been replaced.  Lot is .46 acre and sits in a cul-de-sac.
